title: In bitcoin price plummet, ETF flows are down but aren't signaling 'crypto winter' investor panic
summary_full: As the price of bitcoin and other cryptocurrencies has crashed, exchange-traded funds have seen outflows, but ETF selling doesn't look like investor panic.
summary_public: As the price of bitcoin and other cryptocurrencies has crashed, exchange-traded funds have seen outflows, but ETF selling doesn't look like investor panic.
